                     <interp inst="t18300916-148-person1276" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was detained, and the property given to me.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence, denying that the handkerchief was ever in his possession, or that he was behind the prosecutor, but stood before him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-148-person1277">
